    :alt: Documentation
    :target: https://docs.weblate.org/en/latest/schemas.html

Installation
------------

Install using pip:

.. code-block:: sh

    pip3 install weblate_schemas

Sources are available at <https://github.com/WeblateOrg/weblate_schemas>.

